    public class SelionRemoteIOSDriver
extends org.uiautomation.ios.client.uiamodels.impl.RemoteIOSDriver
implements SeLionIOSBridgeDriver
    SelionRemoteIOSDriver provides facility to add custom CommandExecutor to RemoteIOSDriver . This class also implements the SeLionIOSBridgeDriver interface to expose methods for UIAElement and its subclasses.
